(36, 'wc-admin-learn-more-about-variable-products', 'info', 'en_US', 'Learn more about variable products', 'Variable products are a powerful product type that lets you offer a set of variations on a product, with control over prices, stock, image and more for each variation. They can be used for a product like a shirt, where you can offer a large, medium and small and in different colors.', '{}', 'unactioned', 'woocommerce-admin', '2022-01-25 13:25:59', NULL, 0, 'plain', '', 0, 0, 'info');
